text: "This Charming Man" is a 1983 song by English indie rock band The Smiths and is the second single from the band. It went to number 15 in New Zealand, number 52 in Australia in 1984 and in 1992 it went to number 8 in the United Kingdom and number 9 in Ireland. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1983 songs Category:Jangle pop songs Category:Indie pop songs Category:Death Cab for Cutie songs
title: This Charming Man
